          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Defending Educational Opportunities for West Virginia Students Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to: (1) notify TRIO program applicants of any minor budgeting error in their applications, (2) permit the applicants to resubmit corrected applications no later than 30 days after being notified of the error, and (3) review and score the corrected applications.</p>]]></text>
